profiles:
Summary Over 30 years of experience in High-Tech: 10 years as a SW engineer before moving into sales & executive positions. Today, owns Agip Technologies Ltd, a Management & business coaching company. 

Examples of current activities:  
A Board Member at CrossReader Ltd.  

Examples of recent activities: 
A consultant at Celltick Technologies Ltd., a mobile broadcasting company; 
A consultant at Alvarion Ltd. (Nasdaq: ALVR), the WiMax leader ; 
A consultant at Clariton Networks, a Cellular & CATV convergence company;  
A board member at Evolven, an enterprise SW startup; 
An active Chairman of BeeFence, a security startup; 
A Business Coach at TIM - A Technion subsidiary for Executives development; 
A Venture Partner at Yozma Group, a Venture Capital firm from Tel-Aviv, Israel; 
A consultant at JVP, a Venture Capital firm from Jerusalem, Israel; 
An advisory Board member at Riverhead Networks,which was acquired by Cisco; 
A consultant at Magifire Ltd. which was acquired by F5 inc; 

Prior to this. Joseph spent 9 years and served as a Director of Operations at Cisco Systems Europe where he led and put the foundations for the operations in many countries in the Near/Middle East and in the Eastern Europe regions. 

Before that, he was the Director for South Europe at LanOptics (NASDAQ:LNOP), a LAN Switch/Hub manufacturer. 

From 1986 to 1992, Joseph was employed with DEC Israel . Prior to DEC, Joseph was employed by other leading IT companies. Among others he was the CIO at Elbit Computers Ltd. (NASDAQ:ESLT) for four years and a Sales Manager with IBM for 3 years. 

Joseph holds a B.Sc. in Computer Science and Applied Math from the Technion - Israel Institute of Technology and participated in the MBA / Executives program at IMD, Lausanne, Switzerland. Specialties:Management coaching, Sales and Marketing consulting, Mergers and Aquisition consulting Summary Over 30 years of experience in High-Tech: 10 years as a SW engineer before moving into sales & executive positions. Today, owns Agip Technologies Ltd, a Management & business coaching company. 

